description: This package contains a number of basic plugins to kick start your DjangoCMS project, such as Twitter Bootstrap navbar and buttons, Facebook and Twitter buttons, a Style Modifier, Google Analytics tracking code, Google fonts, meta tags and resiable pictures.

info.Keywords:: button meta twitter bootstrap style modifier racing tadpole
